From:

Subject: FW: DVR Update 
Date: Mon, 09 Mar 2020 21:59:42 +0000 
Special Agent 
FBI New York Field Office 
Violent Crimes Task Force 
From: 
Sent: Tuesda Se tember 17 2019 12:43 PM 
To: 
Cc: 
Subject: DVR Update 
Just got an update from OTD, Digital Forensic Analysis Unit (DFAU), 
DVR 1  has been up and running since the last update. DFAU received the password from the MCC Contractor 
earlier this morning. They are reviewing the data now. (NFI) 
DVR 2 (the cameras that covered the MCC SHU) is currently not running. The MCC Contractor has been 
approved to enter the OTD Lab and start working with DFAU tomorrow to get DVR 2 running. More to follow... 
pedal gent 
FBI New York I  C-19 
Violent Crimes Task Force 
EFTA00017948
